msgid "Sasai"
msgstr "Sasai"

msgctxt "72_The Florist"
msgid "...Had some time to take it all in?"
msgstr "... ¿Pudiste procesar todo?"

msgctxt "84_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. I owe ya one."
msgstr "Sí. Te lo agradezco."

msgctxt "96_Saejima"
msgid "Thanks for lettin' me see him again."
msgstr "Gracias. Por dejarme verlo de nuevo."

msgctxt "108_The Florist"
msgid "A deal's a deal. So, what will you do now?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿qué harás ahora?"

msgctxt "120_Saejima"
msgid "There's one more thing I gotta find out."
msgstr "Hay una cosa más que necesito averiguar..."

msgctxt "132_The Florist"
msgid "You mean Majima?"
msgstr "¿Majima?"

msgctxt "144_Saejima"
msgid "Yeah. I gotta know what really happened back in '85.\\r\n"\n"I wanna hear it straight from his mouth."
msgstr "Sí, necesito saber lo que realmente pasó hace 25 años.\\r\n"\n"Quiero escucharlo directamente de su boca."

msgctxt "156_Saejima"
msgid "Have I spent half my life behind bars for nothing?\\r\n"\n"I can't go out without knowin'."
msgstr "Quiero saber si todos esos 25 años fueron en vano.\\r\n"\n"Sin eso, no podré descansar en paz, incluso si muero."

msgctxt "168_The Florist"
msgid "That reminds me. You broke yourself out of prison, right?\\r\n"\n"It would seem the police are hot on your trail."
msgstr "Entiendo. Eres un fugitivo, ¿verdad?\\r\n"\n"Parece que la policía tiene información de que te vieron en Kamurocho."

msgctxt "180_The Florist"
msgid "I heard they got wind of you being sighted in Kamurocho.\\r\n"\n"The city's crawling with cops right now."
msgstr "La policía está por todas partes, te recomiendo\\r\n"\n"que te escondas hasta que todo se calme."

msgctxt "192_Saejima"
msgid "Shit..."
msgstr "Mierda..."

msgctxt "204_The Florist"
msgid "You'd better lay low until things calm down.\\r\n"\n"You still have that hideout, don't you?"
msgstr "¿Tienes un escondite, verdad?"

msgctxt "216_Saejima"
msgid "Yep."
msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "228_The Florist"
msgid "Then wait it out there for a while. You should be safe\\r\n"\n"from the police as long as you stay underground."
msgstr "Quédate aquí por un tiempo. Deberías estar a salvo si estás en el subterráneo."

msgctxt "240_The Florist"
msgid "You look big enough to handle a manhole cover. Use those\\r\n"\n"to access the sewers and you'll be able to move freely."
msgstr "Seguro que puedes levantar la tapa del alcantarillado.\\r\n"\n"Sal por ahí y regresa al subterráneo de Kamurocho."

msgctxt "252_The Florist"
msgid "Right outside here, there's an entrance to an underground\\r\n"\n"passage. It'll take you to one of Kamurocho's manholes."
msgstr "Hay una entrada que conduce a las alcantarillas justo al salir de aquí."

msgctxt "264_The Florist"
msgid "I suggest using those manholes wherever you find them.\\r\n"\n"They'll help you get back to your hideout undetected."
msgstr "También hay otras alcantarillas en Kamurocho a las que puedes acceder. Úsalas sabiamente para regresar a tu escondite."

msgctxt "276_Saejima"
msgid "Gotcha, thanks."
msgstr "Muy bien, gracias."

msgctxt "300_The Florist"
msgid "That \"deathmatch\" back at the Underground Coliseum?\\r\n"\n"It was a test."
msgstr "¿La \"pelea a muerte\" del coliseo? Fue solo una prueba."

msgctxt "312_Saejima"
msgid "What's that s'posed to mean?"
msgstr "¿Una prueba?"

msgctxt "324_The Florist"
msgid "I wanted to see how you'd act under those circumstances.\\r\n"\n"I hope you don't hold it against me, but it was necessary."
msgstr "Sí, quería ver como actuabas en una situación como esa.\\r\n"\n"No lo tomes a mal."

msgctxt "336_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "348_The Florist"
msgid "Relax. Ivan will survive. Hell, he'll be back in the ring\\r\n"\n"in a week at most."
msgstr "Tranquilo. El hombre que peleó contra ti estará bien.\\r\n"\n"Está en el hospital."

msgctxt "360_The Florist"
msgid "But for now, he's in the hospital. That was quite a beating\\r\n"\n"you gave him."
msgstr "Se está recuperando de menuda paliza."

msgctxt "372_Saejima"
msgid "Least I know he's alright."
msgstr "Por lo menos sé que está bien."

msgctxt "384_The Florist"
msgid "Now, as for that request about your patriarch's fate\\r\n"\n"following that incident 25 years ago."
msgstr "Bien, ahora sobre tu petición. Lo que le pasó a Sasai\\r\n"\n"después de ese incidente de hace 25 años."

msgctxt "396_The Florist"
msgid "After Sasai stepped down in 1985, the Ueno Seiwa Clan\\r\n"\n"put a hit on him, forcing him to go into hiding."
msgstr "Hace 25 años, después de retirarse, Sasai\\r\n"\n"comenzó a ser blanco del clan Ueno Seiwa.\\r\n"\n"Por lo tanto, tuvo que esconderse."

msgctxt "408_Saejima"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "420_The Florist"
msgid "Several months later, someone brought him down here\\r\n"\n"to Purgatory, but he was barely clinging to life."
msgstr "Unos meses después, alguien trajo a Sasai,\\r\n"\n"medio muerto al Purgatorio."

msgctxt "432_The Florist"
msgid "He's been living on the streets since then."
msgstr "Y así, Sasai se convirtió en un vagabundo."

msgctxt "444_Saejima"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "456_Saejima"
msgid "You're tellin' me Sasai-san's still alive?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿el jefe sigue vivo?"

msgctxt "468_The Florist"
msgid "Yes. It was all we could do to keep him from dying.\\r\n"\n"He's homeless now, but he's still in Kamurocho."
msgstr "Sí... A pesar de casi perder la vida y ser un vagabundo.\\r\n"\n"Sigue en Kamurocho."

msgctxt "480_Saejima"
msgid "I see."
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "492_The Florist"
msgid "That said..."
msgstr "Pero..."

msgctxt "504_Saejima"
msgid "What?"
msgstr "¿Qué?"

msgctxt "516_The Florist"
msgid "He's probably－how shall I say－not the man you remember."
msgstr "Cómo decirlo... Él ya no es el Sasai que recuerdas."

msgctxt "528_Saejima"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

msgctxt "540_The Florist"
msgid "I'll have him brought over right now."
msgstr "... Lo traeré ahora mismo."

msgctxt "552_Saejima"
msgid "Here?"
msgstr "¿Caminar, dices?"

msgctxt "564_The Florist"
msgid "Yeah, that's right. Bring him in."
msgstr "Sí, así es. Tráiganlo."

msgctxt "636_Saejima"
msgid " ......"
msgstr " ......"

msgctxt "660_Saejima"
msgid "That... That's him?"
msgstr "... ¿Je-Jefe?"

msgctxt "708_Sasai"
msgid "Ngh..."
msgstr "Ngh..."

msgctxt "720_The Florist"
msgid "Do you know who brought Sasai down here, half dead,\\r\n"\n"a quarter century ago? It was Goro Majima."
msgstr "Hace 25 años, fue Majima quien trajo\\r\n"\n"a Sasai, en estado crítico, a este lugar."

msgctxt "732_Saejima"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

msgctxt "744_The Florist"
msgid "I can only assume Majima was trying to protect Sasai\\r\n"\n"from the Ueno Seiwa Clan after you were gone."
msgstr "Mi teoría es que trató de protegerlo del clan Ueno Seiwa en tu lugar."

msgctxt "756_Sasai"
msgid "Ah... Ohhh..."
msgstr "Ah... Ohhh..."

msgctxt "768_Saejima"
msgid "Sasai-san..."
msgstr "Sasai-san..."

